            <lg xml:id="TK600">
<l>uramoruvaṟ kuḷḷa veṟukkaiyaḵ tillār </l>
<l> maramakka ḷātalē vēṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Energy is mental wealth those men who are destitute of it are only trees in the form of men.</l>
